| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1877 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 961c0c6f-1257-5f6f-ab7d-fa1fa369d576"
